<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Tara Rose Salon — Saadiyat Branch Reviews</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --rose: #c9856a;
    --rose-light: #f5ebe6;
    --rose-deep: #a0614a;
    --gold: #c4a882;
    --dark: #1a1410;
    --mid: #4a3f38;
    --light: #fdf8f5;
    --cream: #f7efe8;
    --border: #e8d8cc;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    background: var(--light);
    color: var(--dark);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  header {
    background: var(--dark);
    padding: 60px 40px 50px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,133,106,0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
  }

  .header-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .branch-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rose);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,133,106,0.4);
    padding: 6px 18px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  header h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  header h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--rose); }

  header p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  .stats-bar {
    background: var(--cream);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 48px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat { text-align: center; }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--rose-deep);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .stat-divider { width: 1px; height: 40px; background: var(--border); }

  .breakdown { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; }

  .breakdown-pill {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pill-green { background: #e8f5e9; color: #2e7d32; }
  .pill-yellow { background: #fff8e1; color: #f57f17; }
  .pill-red { background: #fce4ec; color: #c62828; }

  .filter-bar {
    padding: 24px 40px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 10;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .filter-btn {
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    background: transparent;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--mid);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .filter-btn:hover, .filter-btn.active { background: var(--dark); border-color: var(--dark); color: #fff; }
  .filter-btn.active-pos { background: #2e7d32; border-color: #2e7d32; color: #fff; }
  .filter-btn.active-neg { background: #c62828; border-color: #c62828; color: #fff; }

  .main {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px;
  }

  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .section-header:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

  .section-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .icon-pos { background: #e8f5e9; }
  .icon-neg { background: #fce4ec; }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .section-count {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .reviews-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }

  .review-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .review-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .review-card.negative { border-left: 3px solid #e57373; }
  .review-card.positive { border-left: 3px solid #81c784; }

  .review-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .reviewer-avatar {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose), var(--gold));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .reviewer-info { flex: 1; }

  .reviewer-name {
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .review-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .review-date { font-size: 12px; color: #999; }

  .stars { display: flex; gap: 2px; }
  .star { font-size: 13px; }
  .star.filled { color: #f4b942; }
  .star.empty { color: #ddd; }

  .source-badge {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #4285f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .review-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
  }

  .stylist-tags {
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .stylist-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    background: var(--rose-light);
    color: var(--rose-deep);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .section-sep {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent);
    margin: 8px 0 32px;
  }

  footer {
    background: var(--dark);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  footer span { color: var(--rose); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .stats-bar { gap: 24px; padding: 20px; }
    .stat-divider { display: none; }
    header { padding: 40px 20px 36px; }
    .filter-bar { padding: 16px 20px; }
    .main { padding: 32px 16px; }
    .review-card { padding: 18px 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="branch-tag">Saadiyat Branch</div>
    <h1>Tara Rose <em>Salon</em></h1>
    <p>Client Reviews &amp; Testimonials — Google</p>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value">4.8 / 5</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Google Rating</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-divider"></div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value">667</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Total Reviews</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-divider"></div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-label" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Reputation Breakdown</div>
    <div class="breakdown">
      <span class="breakdown-pill pill-green">95% Positive</span>
      <span class="breakdown-pill pill-yellow">1% Neutral</span>
      <span class="breakdown-pill pill-red">4% Negative</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="filter-bar">
  <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterReviews('all', this)">All Reviews</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterReviews('positive', this)">⭐ 5-Star</button>
  <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterReviews('negative', this)">👎 Low Ratings</button>
</div>

<div class="main">

  <!-- 5 STAR SECTION -->
  <div class="section-header" data-section="positive">
    <div class="section-icon icon-pos">⭐</div>
    <div class="section-title">5-Star Reviews</div>
    <div class="section-count">34 reviews</div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-sep"></div>
  <div class="reviews-grid" id="positive-reviews">

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">S</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Square Limited</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">13 days ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I did Manicure with Mimi and I'm very happy with her service 😍 she did perfect manicure. -KAYA</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Mimi</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">E</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Eli Corcoles</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">a month ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Amazing pedicure and manicure from Sania and Rovina. Amazing work, so I will come back! 💖🫂</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Sania</span><span class="stylist-tag">Rovina</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">A</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Amna Mohammed</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">a month ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I'm someone who values the overall experience as much as the service itself. I first visited the Khalifa City branch of Tara Rose for a haircut and later joined their Silver Package, a monthly membership for hair treatments. The stylists are highly qualified. I used to go to May in Khalifa City and now see Eds at the Saadiyat branch for my weekly treatment and blowout. Eds is an absolute gem — she is incredibly skilled, kind, and truly passionate about what she does. She takes the time to understand your hair and always makes sure you leave feeling your best. The entire team at Saadiyat is warm and welcoming, and the salon itself is beautiful. Highly recommend!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Eds</span><span class="stylist-tag">May</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">S</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Sandra Abbrederis</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">a month ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">(Translated by Google) I have very straight hair, and cutting layers is quite difficult. Tammy is a great technician at it. The way my hair falls is fantastic, and my bangs are perfect. (Original) Ich habe ganz gerade Haare und Stufen zu schneiden ist ziemlich schwer…. Tammy ist eine gute Technikerin darin. Der Haarfall ist super und der Pony ist perfekt.</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Tammy</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">T</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Tanya Zialcita</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">2 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Tara Rose has been my go-to for years. I've had the pleasure to have Tammy do an Ash Beige balayage for my hair which I fully trusted her to do based on her recommendation. She knows what's up. Her expertise, knowledge and style really made all the difference. Especially having her walk me through the entire experience, from understanding what I wanted, the process itself to finally seeing the results was so reassuring. All the staff are so friendly and welcoming too. Highly recommend!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Tammy</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">R</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Rosalie Tonkin</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">2 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Arni agreed to do my nail art and she did it exactly like I wanted it. I'm quite fussy so I was super pleased</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Arni</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">Z</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Zahra Khan</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">2 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I genuinely feel like a new woman! I had the wonderful and bubbly Holly cutting and styling my hair today. After chatting to me about my hair goals and current routine, she added wispy bangs and beautiful layers. Holly also added a hair mask treatment which has truly saved my hair from the daily sun, salt, and chlorine exposure 😊 I loved the little snacks and beverages and the team was so professional and warm. I will definitely be returning and asking for Holly next time!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Holly</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">S</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">shai</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">2 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I had such a great haircut experience with Holly. Hands down the BEST hairdresser I have ever met!!! She transformed my hair into exactly what I imagined it to look like. I absolutely loved her work, she's very talented. The salon and all the staff were very friendly and welcoming. I loved the vibes and I'm definitely going there again.</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Holly</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">S</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Suchita Patel</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">2 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I had a great experience with April! She did a fantastic job in advising me on various colour and cut options, and guiding me on what would suit me best. I'd definitely recommend her!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">April</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">C</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Colleen Jewel Uy</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">3 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Very friendly staff, especially, Ms. Reda and Arnie. Such a good experience and environment. 😊😊</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Reda</span><span class="stylist-tag">Arnie</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">C</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Charlotte Allseybrook</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">3 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Perfect brow lamination and lash lift with Mona as always. Would highly recommend.</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Mona</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">K</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Kristine Saldava</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">3 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Sania is the best facial specialist in the world!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Sania</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Marina Shevchenko</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">3 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">Huge thank you to Molly for the most beautiful hair coloring! She's incredibly talented, attentive to detail, and really knows what she's doing. The result was even better than I expected — truly a 10/10 experience. Highly recommend Molly and this salon!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Molly</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="5">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">C</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
          <div class="reviewer-name">Cyr Lorzano</div>
          <div class="review-meta">
            <div class="stars"><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span></div>
            <span class="review-date">4 months ago</span>
            <div class="source-badge">G</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-text">I did my hair Color with Eds and I supper loved it! Her hair consultation is spot on and delivered. Love the outcome and her product recommendations. Salon is nice, all staff are very accommodating, plus the salon has an amazing view by the beach too!</div>
      <div class="stylist-tags"><span class="stylist-tag">Eds</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="review-card positive" data-rating="4">
      <div class="review-top">
        <div class="reviewer-avatar">M</div>
        <div class="reviewer-info">
